est/authorities/html/90155758">Base de bibliothèque norvégienne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://katalog.nsk.hr/F/?func=direct&amp;doc_number=000037836&amp;local_base=nsk10">Bibliothèque universitaire de Zagreb</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n79-144786">WorldCat</a></span></li></ul></div></li>
