earch/go/document.jsp?id=00000004460">Munzinger Archiv</a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://oregonencyclopedia.org/articles/pauling_linus_1901_1994_/"><i>The Oregon Encyclopedia</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://snl.no/Linus_Pauling"><i>Store norske leksikon</i></a></li>
